If I ever get married, I want to look at my wife the way he looks at her. He’s absolutely mesmerized by her and as he should be. Their chemistry is palpable. Her musical chops are also brilliant. This is a clip with Caterina Valente on the Dean Martin show.

We have a responsibility to relish in our triumphs… Humility is one thing; nevertheless, gratitude is the product of recognition. Special shouts @mattdavella for this interview. Full interview is in the link in my bio. #tbt

Huge shouts to @aliciakeys for personally calling Prince’s camp and convincing them to allow me to cover this song. Not only did she do that, she let me play her actual piano that night. One of the top moments of my life. My grandson, then 10 months, watching me sing. I love how it took him a second to realize it was me, then to notice it wasn’t a FaceTime. Lastly, to sit back and start listening… That’s my daughter holding the iPad and her mom in the background. This was a great day
#tbt Best Part. Forgot the words for a second hahaha  #musician #singer #artist #piano #goodvibes

Words can't express the heartbreak I feel right now. I was watching this clip just last night for the millionth time, never assuming I'd never get to talk to you ever again. We've played together countless times throughout our career. Aaron was the one that we all admired from very early on. I was a teenager going to shed in the basement and I didn't even play drums. I remember one time Aaron invited me to sit down with him and he taught me some things. His gift was a big as his heart. We love you, brother. Long Live Aaron Spears #aaronspears
Cheers

Due to the overwhelming love from my last post, here's the performance. I can't thank you all enough for your love, support and kind words over these years. Thank you. Thank you. Thank you. I composed this original version for my friends' wedding a year or so before I got the call to be on the show. After which, I dedicated it to my daughter. Talk about full circle. Cheers #teamterrence #music #love #art #thevoice #mygirl
